[I] A virtio-fs vhost-user device daemon written in Rust

[T] This program is a vhost-user backend that implements the virtio-fs device.
[T] Each virtio-fs device instance requires its own virtiofsd process.

[U] https://gitlab.com/virtio-fs/virtiofsd/

